story.text: Well. It has been a while. New Shape submission was a wild ride. And it is done. I am proud no matter how it is received. It is good work no matter what anyone says.
I need to send a copy to Ward and a few others for review. I am very interested to see what Tom will think.
I am subtly impressed that I managed to complete the project with so few resources and while working a day job and a start-up.
